    {
      "id": "6a470a5afb5d690a421e16e8",
      "text": "又",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1783040604,
      "updated": 1783040604
    },
    {
      "id": "6a470a2a0000000000b5598f",
      "text": " 「[メタ]」（英語：meta-）の[希哲館訳語][hiro.icon]",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1783040604,
      "updated": 1783040632
    },
    {
      "id": "6a470a420000000000b55991",
      "text": "  メとタの[合字]（合略仮名）に見えることに気付いた",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1783040628,
      "updated": 1783041175
    },
    {
      "id": "6a470d900000000000b55995",
      "text": "   「[メタを「又」と訳せることに気付く https://dlt.kitetu.com/KNo.F85E/0CC0]」がもう10年以上も前かあ……",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1783041475,
      "updated": 1783041517
    },
    {
      "id": "6a470a2b0000000000b55990",
      "text": "  「○○についての○○」の再帰性・間接性を「また」と解釈できる",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1783040606,
      "updated": 1783041332
    },
    {
      "id": "6a470d040000000000b55994",
      "text": "   又貸し・又聞きなどに使われる接頭辞としての役割を拡張",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1783041335,
      "updated": 1783041455
    },
    {
      "id": "6a470a900000000000b55992",
      "text": "  又認知（メタ認知）、又情報（メタ情報）、又言語（メタ言語）……",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1783040707,
      "updated": 1783041062
    },
